## Sales Prediction

This project predicts product sales using machine learning techniques as part of the CodSoft Data Science Internship.

### Dataset
The dataset contains advertising expenditure on TV, Radio, and Newspaper along with sales data.

### Model Used
Linear Regression

### Tools & Technologies
Python  
Pandas  
Scikit-learn  

### Evaluation Metrics
Mean Absolute Error (MAE)  
Mean Squared Error (MSE)

### Result
The model predicts sales with reasonable accuracy based on advertising expenditure.
